reviewText: Season 19 was excellent in all respects.  One of my friends was a team member as one of the teams in Season 19.  My only complaint, and it's a MINOR complaint is that the video quality could have been a little bit clearer in definition, and hopefully was corrected in the Blu-ray edition for a clearer display.

This is the second season of The Amazing Race that I have ordered from Amazon where the audio is out of sync with the video. It is like watching a dubbed Japanese movie. I'm not sure why this is a recurring problem
This DVD came in unable to play AT ALL. I couldn't be any more unhappy. Thus, it is going back.

This was a really great season of Amazing Race though not the best one I've seen but still great. The cover should have included all participants from the race so as to not arouse suspicion or give away the surviving teams.
Love the series and look forward to each season as released.
